The '''Accademia di Belle Arti "Mario Sironi" di Sassari''' is an academy of fine arts located in [[Sassari]], [[Sardinia]]. It was founded in 1989 and it is the more recently established Italian state academy of fine art.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Giovanna Cassese|title= Accademie Patrimoni di Belle Arti|publisher=Gangemi, 2013|isbn=8849276710}}</ref>

